messages.cookiePage.title: Manage Cookies
messages.cookiePage.paragraph1: You can use this page to manage which cookies are set on your browser or mobile device, but if you disable cookies, some parts this website may not function as some cookies are essential.
messages.cookiePage.paragraph2: To disable cookies used by this website for personalised advertising you will need to follow all steps below.
messages.cookiePage.header: Step 1: Advertising based on your use of our site
messages.cookiePage.paragraph3: We help you see advertisements with products and services that are relevant to you, based on your characteristics, your online activity and your interests
messages.cookiePage.paragraph4: If you turn this off, you will still see the SAME number of advertisements but they may be less relevant
messages.cookiePage.paragraph5: You may continue to see ads that are targeted to you based on other information.
messages.cookiePage.paragraph6: By clicking the button below you are accepting cookies in accordance with our Cookie Policy
messages.cookiePage.header2: Step 2: Ads based on your online activity
messages.cookiePage.paragraph7: Third party cookies are used on our website to serve you with ads to remind you of the products you have seen on our site. You may see these advertisements on other sites that you visit. You can opt out of our use of these cookies using the options below.
messages.cookiePage.paragraph8: Follow the links below for each site's policies and instructions to opt out:
messages.cookiePage.paragraph9: You will need to make these changes on every browser you use.
messages.cookiePage.googlePartner: Google is our main advertising platform and is also used by some advertisers to buy adverts that appear on our Sites.
messages.cookiePage.googleAds: Advertising systems that some advertisers use to buy adverts on our Sites.
messages.cookiePage.header3: Step 3: Third party cookies that help us deliver other functionality
messages.cookiePage.paragraph10: We also use third party cookies to optimize marketing performance and to measure the effectiveness of our advertising on other websites. This might include:
messages.cookiePage.manageCookiesGoogle: Manage Cookies with Google Ad Settings
messages.cookiePage.manageCookiesAdChoices: Manage Cookies with Your Ad Choices
messages.cookiePage.manageCookiesLinkedIn: Manage Cookies with LinkedIn Cookie Table
